Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 又睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好睡覺腦子會壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還是搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明明收拾掉了那個妖狐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,身體還是沒有復原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,尋找 斬殺 直到復原為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,自從離開醍醐你太逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好休息光顧著斬妖除魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.71,0:01:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去身體吃不消…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,現在威脅國家安危的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,才是鬼神！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說沒了爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也要好好活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我會陪著大哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,白面不動之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在那座山對面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,謝啦 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有溫泉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,山上會自己湧出熱水喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去那裡的話大哥哥也能好好休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽說溫泉不僅能讓身體放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,還能讓心情平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,總之我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,傳言那溫泉附近有妖怪出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,朝倉軍隊已退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,又降恩惠之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還不能解除和鬼神的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是我老婆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,果然這張臉也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在這過夜再合適不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找點木柴和果子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 這裡說不定是強盜的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不能殺掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,教訓一下就行了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,撿了很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,瀑布的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？好大的佛像…別嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我很難吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而且百鬼丸大哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是多羅羅啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,別拽了好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 看看這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫阿鰹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,阿鰹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 這裡是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,阿鰹一個人住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾有路人來瀑布會留下食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我就靠這些為生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛那個瀑布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來為什麼那座佛像沒有臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,以前有位武士來到瀑布前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,發現了被沖刷成不動尊形狀的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,本來那位武士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就因為雕刻的佛像面容安詳而聞名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是到了武士時代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,人們開始敬仰威風滿面的不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,於是這位武士逐漸被人遺忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,武士想要再次得到大家的青睞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,開始在岩石上雕刻不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,身體 手 腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,到最後雕刻臉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,武士下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要雕刻出前所未有最威風的不動尊臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,雕刻出的臉全都似曾相識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,雕刻完又毀掉 長年累月周而復始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,武士慢慢變老
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最終也沒能完成 抱憾而終
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這故事聽不太懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,對多羅羅來說還太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哇看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,來 請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看到這粥我想起了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來你把我叫做媽媽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我長得特別像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼看都是我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,連聲音都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟最近都沒好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吵醒他好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡晚上很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 第一次吃到這麼好吃的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我…還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你媽媽可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,比起阿鰹 還是媽媽更合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅真是愛撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以喔 你喜歡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我在喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,安心下來之後我好像也睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 我還擔心藥不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛那位武士的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,還有後續喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那位武士死後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不動尊不知何時被妖怪依附了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,為了完成武士的遺願
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想要一張臉 想要一張臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不動尊復活了武士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,命令她把活人帶過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為了把人臉獻給不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是那位武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,通過不動尊的力量讀取對方的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就能隨意改變自己的相貌與聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的臉不適合不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果是那個男人的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅真是愛撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就把這張臉獻給不動尊吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等著我 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我這就去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,把大哥哥還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我都沒有捆住你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對不會把大哥哥交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你放開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我發誓要跟隨大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,睡得真香啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧 百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有必要毀掉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那個聲音 是大哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 來媽媽身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是阿鰹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…為什麼我的臉沒有變？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道自己母親的相貌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:15:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,把臉給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在尋找這張臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要他的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,至今為止找到的最好的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼非要這麼好的臉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有眼睛 有牙齒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,還有嘴巴 這已經足夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是阿鰹卻肆意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,變成了一個欺騙別人 掠奪人臉的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你考慮一下被扒下臉的人的感受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,難受 不甘 傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,比所有的不動尊都好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,從何時開始 從何時開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,從何時開始 我變成了這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,放在你的臉上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對我笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個溫柔的孩子 多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就像佛陀一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想自己先振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,卻增加了你的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,還讓你想起了母親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然大哥哥一直在幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你遇到困難的話 我絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉附近有妖怪出現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,其實是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,當時…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 這裡這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 我還是第一次泡溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看喔 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然知道你看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛…滲進傷口了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是所謂極樂吧 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就此死去也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和尚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你從哪裡出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,聽你這語氣真是過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在你們來之前就在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 這就是孽緣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 洗澡了 洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,洗澡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:20:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你們幹什麼 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他們一直都很淘氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你從哪裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這附近沒見過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,旅行？ 要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是要去哪個地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…我還沒想好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人是你的哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥就是大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你的背上好像寫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要老盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這是地圖吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,地圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,地圖 是地圖！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這絕對是地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:21:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要老盯著人家身體看！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係吧 讓我們看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了 看到了…
